Olivia Barash https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olivia_Barash 0 Olivia Barash (born January 11, 1965, in Miami, Florida) is an American actress. As an adult, she has appeared in films, including the cult film Repo Man, and on television as a child actress, including Little House on the Prairie, Charlie's Angels, Soap, and as an adult in Fame, and St. Elsewhere. She appeared in the pilot episode of The Incredible Hulk (as a little girl whom the Hulk saves from drowning in a lake).
